  <brief_title>Neuromuscular Electrical Stimulation Cycling</brief_title>
  <official_title>Interactive Cycling System Using Electromyography (EMG)-Driven Neuromuscular Electrical Stimulation (NMES) for Rehabilitation</official_title>
